<P><HI>Now the day is actually come which burns as an oven, and all the proud</HI> (all infidels) <HI>and all that do wickedly</HI> (all impenitent &s;inners) <HI>&s;hall be as &s;tubble: the day is come that &s;hall burn them up, and leave them neither root nor branch.</HI></P>
